{"tid":1888434,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy S20 120Hz@1440p 將通過更新釋出","createTime":"2020-02-20T07:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T05:39:29.000Z","uid":29880,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a8648b2d20d29e1c419f39b36d1af1f8250ea06","tid":1888434,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"XDA Developers 網站的 Max Weinbach 昨日在 Twitter 爆料，表示 Samsung 正在為 Galaxy S20 系列的系統進行改善，包括將 120Hz 屏幕刷新率同時應用於 1440p 解像度，如果開發和測試過程順利的話，就會通過系統更新的形式推送予所有 Galaxy S20 系列手機，預計在未來 1 至 3 個月會完成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-02/20/215252/uniqlo_1_81220ef7a2d2ca987ce7575f6ab11b7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-02%2F20%2F215252%2Funiqlo_1_81220ef7a2d2ca987ce7575f6ab11b7d.jpg&h=dd274ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智能手機越高階，效能就越強，但廠商往往無法在新機上市之時，將所有新功能一次過提供。除了因為開發和測試需時，部份進階功能或會導致更耗電，或影響手機的穩定性，在上市初期暫時收起，一來可以減少因為新功能引發的投訴，二來透過更新推出新功能亦讓用戶對廠商有更好的印象，同時為手機保持新鮮感，亦有望吸引未入手的消費者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/215252/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F215252%2F1%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=2eac1cff\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/215252/1/</a>"},{"pid":"27c03ffa1bdf0f652f96633a9fb82d8f4f9fc184","tid":1888434,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T21:18:46.000Z","msg":"2k呢"},{"pid":"48f28cd25af330e12325a78f58e3c8bdeff283fa","tid":1888434,"uid":255744,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:28:31.000Z","msg":"前面有1080P例子，人哋俾足6000mAh都唔係捱得耐，你電又少過人，解像度又高過人，仲要行5G。最後要小心柒爆"},{"pid":"cd908e06ac0e37d0ef083db2617c3c28dfe69c2f","tid":1888434,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f28cd25af330e12325a78f58e3c8bdeff283fa","tid":1888434,"uid":255744,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,